  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK852">
<l>pakalkarutip paṟṟā ceyiṉu mikalkaruti</l>
<l>yiṉṉācey yāmai talai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though disagreeable things may be done from (a feeling of) disunion, it is far better that nothing painful be done from (that of) hatred.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
